// STM32F411 UART Printf - Platform Overlay
//
// Extends the base stm32f4.repl by adding:
//   - LED on GPIOA pin 5 (Nucleo LD2)
//
// Note: USART2 is already defined in the base stm32f4.repl platform,
// so we don't need to add it here. We just use showAnalyzer in the .resc
// script to open a terminal window for it.

UserLED: Miscellaneous.LED @ gpioPortA

gpioPortA:
    5 -> UserLED@0